attachments.text:
*Overview*

POST request to endpoint /consultation/consultationId/daily_rounds/analyse/ gives _Permission Denied_ error for read-only users. This endpoint is used for *ABG Analysis Plot* at frontend.

*Steps to reproduce*

1. Login as read-only user (Cred=> username:readonly, password:Welcome@123)
2. Go to patient tab and choose any patient
3. Opening consultation page will give "You Dont have permission..." notfification when logged in as read-only
4. Observe network section in developer option of browser

*Demo*

2022-06-30 00:00:00.text: Working on <https://github.com/ohcnetwork/care_fe/issues/1789|#1789> backend is complete and working, needs some improvement at frontend

attachments.text:
Any facility today cannot fetch data on how many admissions they have had on any day.

The problem is even if they apply the admissions date filters, they can browse through the live list/dischasrged list of patients, but they will not have details or number of patients who were admitted to their facility on such date and they discharged and admitted to / shifted to another facility.

Every facility must have its own registry of a number of admissions across various bed types.

<https://github.com/gigincg|@gigincg>
